Enforcement Administration. Assistant U.S. Attorney John Crabb Jr. 
said DEA agents recovered a 12-gauge shotgun and drug paraphernalia 
after arresting Gray. 
</P>
<P>
	Prosecutors said Gray came to the attention of the DEA last  
spring after another area man was caught with drugs and said Gray 
had provided him with cocaine on at least 70 occasions, prosecutors 
said. 
</P>
<P>
	Gray is one of five sons of Mfume, whose birth name was Frizzell  
Gray. Sentencing was scheduled for Feb. 11. 
  	   	
