                        *Notre Dame 28, Navy 24 	
</P>
<P>
	At South Bend, Ind., Jarious Jackson hit Jay Johnson for a  
16-yard TD pass with 36 seconds left as Notre Dame (5-3) extended 
its NCAA-record winning streak over Navy (2-6) to 36 games with a 
28-24 win. 
</P>
<P>
	The streak seemed all but over with 5:56 left when Tim Shubzda's  
33-yard field goal with 5:56 left put Navy ahead 24-21. 
  	   	
</P>
