<CATEGORY> international </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Hundreds Feared Dead in Cyclone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BALESHWAR, India (AP) -- A cyclone battered a broad swath of  
eastern India for a second day Saturday, knocking out power and 
telephone lines and flattening thousands of homes. 
</P>
<P>
	Hundreds may have died, said officials in Orissa state, which  
