<HEADLINE> Lineup for Sunday TV News Shows  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Lineup for the Sunday TV news shows:  

</P>
<P>
	ABC's ``This Week'' -- Topic: Al Gore's presidential campaign.  
Guest: Vice President Al Gore. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	CBS' ``Face the Nation'' -- Bill Bradley's presidential campaign.  
Guest: Former Sen. Bill Bradley, D-N.J. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	NBC's ``Meet the Press'' -- Topic: Pat Buchanan and the Reform  
Party. Guest: Presidential candidate Pat Buchanan. 

</P>
<P>
