</P>
<P>
	CNN's ``Late Edition'' -- Topics: Reform Party politics, budget  
negotiations and the 2000 election campaign, and campaign ads. 
Guests: Presidential candidate Pat Buchanan, Sens. Charles Schumer, 
D-N.Y., and Orrin Hatch, R-Utah, Republican strategist Ed Rollins 
and Democratic strategist Bob Beckel. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	``Fox News Sunday'' -- Topics: Donald Trump's bid for the White  
House and the federal budget. Guests: Donald Trump and Sens. Mitch 
McConnell, R-Ky., and Harry Reid, D-Nev. 
  	   	
</P>
